# Business Finance Pro - .gitignore

## OS-generated files
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

## Excel temp/lock/backup files
~$*.xlsx
~$*.xlsm
*.tmp
*.xlk
*.bak

## Editor / IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

## Local working copies (keep the release workbook, ignore scratch copies)
/scratch/
/working/
*-copy.xlsx
*-test.xlsx
*_backup.xlsx

## Archives generated during packaging (rebuild from source, don't commit)
*.zip

## Screenshot exports not yet finalized for the guide
/screenshots/raw/
/screenshots/*.psd

## macOS/Windows misc
*.lnk
